      "schema:description": "Version 2: STAG3 coordinate correction. Original analysis used wrong coordinates (chr7:99,819,969-99,895,036) due to an Ensembl REST API error. Correct GRCh38 coordinates confirmed from NCBI Gene ID 10734 are chr7:100,177,724-100,219,334. Corrected files added as stag3_verification.zip. All other 31 gene findings, methodology, and results are unchanged.",
